description: Up In Smoke, that's the right way to make your BBQ! Cooked up in small batches for that fresh quality, their fantastic BBQ and sides will always have you coming back for more! Their homemade rubs and custom lend of woods make every bite taste even better than the last. Up In Smoke's #1 goal is clear, to win the hearts, minds, and stomachs of every last one of their customers!
name: Up In Smoke BBQ
